# 🎵 AI Song Recommendation System

## 📌 Project Description

AI Song Recommendation System is a Python-based application that recommends songs according to the user's preferences. The user selects a genre, mood, and language, and the system displays matching songs from the database.

This project was developed as part of the DecodeLabs AI Internship.

---

## 🚀 Features

- 🎵 Recommend songs based on:
  - Genre
  - Mood
  - Language
- 📋 View all songs
- 🔍 Search songs by name
- ⭐ View top-rated songs
- 🎤 Filter songs by artist
- 🎲 Surprise Me (Random Song Recommendation)
- ❌ Invalid input handling
- 🔄 Menu-driven interface

---

## 🛠 Technologies Used

- Python 3
- Lists
- Dictionaries
- Loops
- Conditional Statements
- Functions
- Random Module

---

